{"tid":1252670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"皇后大道東又變禁歌 被中國數個音樂平台下架","createTime":"2019-06-23T06:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T06:56:53.000Z","uid":77905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47355f908f10ce06f6f13d0f019d6ac171ab7e31","tid":1252670,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:38:33.000Z","msg":"羅大佑作曲、林夕作詞的經典歌曲《皇后大道東》已被中國數個音樂平台下架，另一首歌曲《東方之珠》也被限制評論。香港《蘋果動新聞》記者發現《東方之珠》的評論最後日子是6月12日，有網友留下「自由」、「無奈」、「單曲循環」，惟系統上也不時看到「該評論已刪除」的字句。<br />\n<br />\n《皇后大道東》被視為1990年代的政治歌曲，表現出對當時尚未到來的主權移交的不確定感。羅大佑曾在1991年港台《鏗鏘集》上表示，音樂和政治一樣，都是表達自己不同的意見；「當大家都不敢表達自己，有一個人便會特別大聲，這個人就是專制者」。林夕也曾表示，1997年主權移交後，香港或許不會有這樣自由的創作環境能寫這些題材，所以他要先寫出來。<br />\n<br />\n羅大佑上周六（15日）在台北小巨蛋舉行演唱會，唱到《皇后大道東》時，曾對香港《逃犯條例》風波有感而發，他3度強調「有些事情真的不能那麼急」。<br />\n<br />\n然而網友「Alternative Nation」19日發文並附上網頁截圖指出，目前在QQ音樂、網易雲音樂、酷狗音樂、蝦米音樂都找不到《皇后大道東》。這則帖文隔天也被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n該網友14日還發現，「達明一派」的簡介在豆瓣網站的音樂分類上已搜尋不到結果。今年4月，曾支持佔中的達明一派，其多首歌曲在中國區Apple Music被下架。<br />\n<br />\n另外，羅大佑另一首歌曲《東方之珠》，在QQ音樂網站也被下架，在蝦米音樂則是限制評論。（香港《蘋果動新聞》、大陸中心／報導） <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190623/20710987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190623%2F20710987&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaKpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=658ebb38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190623%2F20710987&h=8983164d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190623/20710987</a>"},{"pid":"95a463df59c624c591e11034af9f559568ddb1a5","tid":1252670,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UYzQEObtujA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUYzQEObtujA&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaKpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=bbd05f66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UYzQEObtujA</a>"},{"pid":"9644a046cd6b0d129a545e85d521fe7de9b67601","tid":1252670,"uid":192052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:46:57.000Z","msg":"祖國強大 世界末日 同希特拉統一全球一樣咁可怕"},{"pid":"89136b3cf774b8c00a9de5082b23e445820a5686","tid":1252670,"uid":186152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"毛澤大道東仲好聽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a70dcc7bd31bb5166c605ea153481d89285ce2","tid":1252670,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89136b3cf774b8c00a9de5082b23e445820a5686","tid":1252670,"uid":186152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"毛澤大道東仲好聽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"下一句：毛澤大盜西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}